rk where lighting is critical, opt for the Nano-texture–but this option adds to the price of the display.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What are the stand options?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Apple offers three types of stands for the Studio Display:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Tilt-adjustable stand</strong>: Allows for only the adjustment of the display’s tilt. This comes standard with the Studio Display.</li><li><strong>Tilt- and height-adjustable stand</strong>: Can adjust the tilt and height. This stand costs extra.</li><li><strong>VESA mount adapter</strong>: Used to attach to a VESA-compatible arm, wall mount, or stand. Comes at no additional cost.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t<h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</h4>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Apple Studio Display</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"2988\" height=\"1992\" src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/apple-studio-display-hero.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Apple Studio Display\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/apple-studio-display-hero.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 2988w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/apple-studio-display-hero.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/apple-studio-display-hero.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/apple-studio-display-hero.jpg?resize=1200%2C800&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/apple-studio-display-hero.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/apple-studio-display-hero.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/apple-studio-display-hero.jpg?resize=